<br>
I am a hunter, but I'm also a conservationist.  Aside from donations, memberships, practicing quality deer managment, and other conservational programs, my $20 dollar deer license probably does more for conservation than most hippy fucks who complain about how inhumane hunting is and why we shouldn't do it.<br>
<br>
